snippet.title: Froot Basket Valentine - Teaser
snippet.description:
A casual reminder that Froot Basket Valentine is not only a Valentines' Day otome game/visual novel, but also a game appropriate for Halloween spoop. But only if you want it to be that way...

Check out the game: https://xxmissarichanxx.itch.io/froot-basket-valentine/

Music: 
- TAM Music Factory, https://www.tam-music.com/
- Kevin MacLeod, https://incompetech.com/

- - -
Ollo~ Itsa me, Ari! I draw and stuff!
